reviewBlob: Sophisticated appeareance with an appropriate carbonatation and a good head retention.  The taste is eclectic.  Strong bitterness and heavy malt but not balance together.
Clean appearence.  Light body but heavy grain bitterness taste.  There is something fizzy at the end.
beerName: Les Bires de la Nouvelle-France Blonde dpeautre

reviewBlob: Very light but not clear.  Not as banana as expected for a kristal weizen.  Body is giving a good shape to the taste.
Good carbonation but no head retention.  One taste dimension: fruity caramel.  Too bad that is no hops aroma to balance it.
